observe.desc:
[
{Sap extracted from a nameless, gigantic tree on the edge of the world. }
]

[
{According to the exploration team, there were large numbers of green colored lifeforms around it. This was because the sap makes them satiated and contained potent healing powers.}
]

[
{However, some of the employees who drank it melted, leaving smoldering, green remains.}
]

[
{Other various experiments confirmed that the probability of melting rapidly increases as more sap is consumed.}
]

[
{“Many wondered how such a large tree could prosper on the barren outskirts. The lifeforms who consumed the sap were its nutrients. The tree reaped from what it sowed.”}
]
